description:
GetThatRory

Get pictures of everyone's favorite cat, Rory!

Adds /rory to get over 100+ random Rory photos from https://rory.cat!
Defaults to a random Rory, but you can also enter an ID.

```
/rory [id] [whisper]
--> very cute cat photo
```

Download:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hauntii/EnPlugins/main/GetThatRory/Release/GetThatRory.js

Source Code: https://github.com/hauntii/EnPlugins/tree/main/GetThatRory/Source
